nodes.text: Boba Fett: From Obscure Villain to Cultural Icon

Boba Fett: From Obscure Villain to Cultural Icon is an article written by Jon Bradley Snyder for Star Wars Insider 30 that examines the immense popularity of the character Boba Fett in the Star Wars fan community. The article offers perspectives from several Star Wars VIPs: Dave Dorman, Jeremy Bulloch, Stephen J. Sansweet, Steve Perry, Anthony Daniels, Tom Veitch, Kathy Tyers, Kevin J. Anderson, and Irvin Kershner.
